subject: Rachel Alexandra (Race Horse)
Horse Racing
lead_paragraph: Rachel Alexandra, who in May became the first filly to win the Preakness Stakes in 85 years, will again face colts in the Haskell Invitational on Aug. 2 at Monmouth Park.
